
                              AMOS Professional
                        NTSC<>PAL Switcher Accessory
                                 By Greg Cox

About ?
~~~~~~~
Welcome to the NTSC<>PAL Switcher Accessory ! 

With this AMOS Professional accessory utility you can change your screen
between NTSC (60Hz) and PAL (50Hz) modes within your AMOS Professional
Editor.

Requirements:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- AMOS Professional
- 1084/1084S compatible monitor or one that can display NTSC and PAL.

How to install ?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Load NTSC<>PAL.AMOS as an accessory via the pull down menu from the Editor.

Or

- You can install it in your pull-down menu via the 'Add Option' or
  [Amiga]+[U] keys. See your AMOS Professional manual (pg. 04.01.28) on how
  to install accessories within the AMOS Professional Editor via the USER
  pull-down menu.

